            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Warning!!! To all the parents reading these school reviews before joining their children in this school , listen carefully, please dont even think of admitting your child in this school, this school absuses children both mentally and physically. Some teachers in this school beat children just for the sake of their cruel personal satisfaction. I am saying all this because, I studied in this school before and i was traumatized.\nThis school will affect your child's mental health for 100% sure.",
