            "name": "Yashaswini"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-05-11",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I think it's one of the best schools in vizag .I have studied here for 14 years . The main asset is ICSE syllabus which serves as a good foundation to students. Standard of teaching is even good .\n\nApart from studies personality development is seen in students. Highly disciplined and teachers are responsible. They provide tremendous support and guide us . Students are encouraged a lot in all aspects such as sports , co curricular activities etc . The English standard spoken by sfs students is commendable and  far better than many other  corporate schools .\n\nRecently they have started junior college which is fabulous. Thanks to my principal , teachers and friends for giving me memories which I can cherish for lifetime  . Miss my school and college .",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
