          "reviewBody": "Worst management, teachers, office staff are also, the ladies in office always show that they are busy, a fatty malayale lady not even used to see the face of parents while talking, manners less lady...... Teachers are using iron scale to beat our children........ They are using negative words like stupid to children, as this school teachers are too brilliant...... Teachers are speaking English, but completely wrong.......... If you have any complaints also the office staff will not allow to meet principal (CM)..... I don't prefer this school.....",
